This programs efficiently takes input from the users and asks them what sort of operation needs to be executed on that.
After doing the calculations in no time, it displays the results to the user and also catches if there are any exceptions or errors.
For example if user tries to divide any integer by 0, the program would crash because of ZeroDivisionError, however, this program,
catches the errors and exceptions and handles them. While also giving a meaningful message to the user.
